{
  "stem": "10272.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they were picked up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were refugees from Romania without ID cards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they told me the story, what is going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That from Romania, also, people are being taken to an area in the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because it was 1941, broke out the war between Russia and Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he didn't want to take care.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He just delayed the whole thing by promising to do it in certain stages, to a little by little do it, not all of them at once.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this story of my best friend, [INAUDIBLE] father, who was also on this transport, he managed to come back from this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was not killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His wife was killed, and one of his daughters killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But his son, [INAUDIBLE], was with me in Budapest at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in jail.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These Romanians told me the story what happened, that these 20,000 Jews Hitler demanded from Hungary to expedite, to deport-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he complied.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He complied with this order.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't know this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just heard the story from them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was already relaxed little bit that I know that my parents-- what my mother's telling me in this postcard-- must have happened during the deportation from our home.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I could make two and two together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But still, I didn't know the whole story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The whole story, only later, after the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I found out exactly from this [INAUDIBLE] father, and from other people who were on that transport, who managed to escape.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because it was very easy, they said, to escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a train. in [INAUDIBLE] a train was deporting, let's say, 500 Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Right?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they went to another station, also deporting.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
